description: Taking happy hour to the streets of Texas, this is a truck you're sure to love.Happy Hour Food Truck has everything you could ask for; burgers, cheese steaks, chicken wings, and more. This is just the kind of filling food you need when you're having a night out in Houston. If you're on the lookout for an awesome way to feed your need on the streets of Texas, then this is the food truck for you!
name: Happy Hour Food
